d 'XTTEST4': module to calculate heterokedasticity tests for fixed effects models
d
d   This package provides new commands for calculating statistics
d for heteroscedasticity in the residuals of fixed effects models
d on panel data. 
d
d KW: heteroskedasticity
d KW: LM statistic
d KW: fixed effects
d
d Requires: Stata version 11
d
d Distribution-Date: 20251119
d
d Author: Manh Hoang Ba, Eureka Uni Team, Vietnam
d Support: email hbmanh9492@@gmail.com
d
f xttest4.ado
f xttest4.sthlp
